canonical:
  title: 途中
  author: 徐居正
  language: lzh
  text: 雨後長途澁馬蹄龍鍾衫袖半霑泥漏雲斜日長林晩無數山禽種種啼
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 途中
  author: 徐居正
  language: lzh
  text: 雨後長途澁馬蹄。龍鍾衫袖半霑泥。漏雲斜日長林晩。無數山禽種種啼。
korean:
  title: 도중
  author: 서거정
  language: kor
  text: |-
    비온 뒤에 긴 길에 말 발굽이 어려워
    구지레한 적삼 소매가 반은 진흙에 젖었다
    구름을 새어 나오는 비낀 해가 먼 숲에 저무는데
    수없는 산새들이 갖가지로 운다
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1450_020_0140&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: On the Road
  author: Seo Geo-jeong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    After the rain, my horse struggles on the long muddy path.
    My worn jacket sleeve hangs heavy, half-soaked in mud.
    Through breaking clouds, the slanting sun fades beyond the distant grove—
    Countless mountain birds cry out in their manifold voices.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The 'worn jacket' (龍鍾衫袖) suggests both the physical weariness of travel and the poet's emotional state, a common technique in classical Chinese poetry where external conditions mirror inner experience.
